autoContrast.description: Determines whether active item text color should depend on background-color of the indicator. If luminosity of the color prop is less than theme.luminosityThreshold, then theme.white will be used for text color, otherwise theme.black. Overrides theme.autoContrast.
autoContrast.description_zh: 确定活动项文本颜色是否应取决于指示器的 background-color。如果 color 属性的亮度小于 theme.luminosityThreshold，则 theme.white 将用于文本颜色，否则使用 theme.black。覆盖 theme.autoContrast。

boundaries.description: Number of elements visible on the left/right edges, 1 by default
boundaries.description_zh: 左/右边缘可见的元素数，默认为 1 个

color.description: Key of theme.colors, active item color, theme.primaryColor by default
color.description_zh: theme.colors 的键，活动项目颜色，默认为 theme.primaryColor

defaultValue.description: Active page for uncontrolled component, must be an integer in [0, total] interval
defaultValue.description_zh: 不受控制组件的活动页，必须是 [0， total] 间隔内的整数

disabled.description: Determines whether all controls should be disabled, false by default
disabled.description_zh: 确定是否应禁用所有控件，默认情况下为 false

gap.description: Key of theme.spacing, gap between controls, 8 by default
gap.description_zh: theme.spacing 的键，控件之间的间隙，默认为 8

getControlProps.description_zh: 将 props 添加到 next/previous/first/last 控件

getItemProps.description: Additional props passed down to controls
getItemProps.description_zh: 传递给控件的其他 props

hideWithOnePage.description: Determines whether the pagination should be hidden when only one page is available (total={1}), false by default
hideWithOnePage.description_zh: 确定当只有一个页面可用时是否应隐藏分页 （total={1}），默认为 false

onFirstPage.description: Called when first page control is clicked
onFirstPage.description_zh: 单击第一个页面控件时调用

onLastPage.description: Called when last page control is clicked
onLastPage.description_zh: 单击最后一个页面控件时调用

onNextPage.description: Called when next page control is clicked
onNextPage.description_zh: 单击下一页控件时调用

onPreviousPage.description: Called when previous page control is clicked
onPreviousPage.description_zh: 单击上一页控件时调用

radius.description: Key of theme.radius or any valid CSS value to set border-radius, numbers are converted to rem, theme.defaultRadius by default
radius.description_zh: key的 theme.radius 或任何有效的 CSS 值来设置 border-radius，数字默认转换为 rem，theme.defaultRadius

siblings.description: Number of siblings displayed on the left/right side of the selected page, 1 by default
siblings.description_zh: 所选页面左侧/右侧显示的同级数量，默认为 1 个

size.description: height and min-width of controls, 'md' by default
size.description_zh: 控件的 height 和 min-width，默认为 'md'

value.description: Active page for controlled component, must be an integer in [0, total] interval
value.description_zh: 受控组件的活动页，必须是 [0， total] 间隔内的整数

withControls.description: Determines whether next/previous controls should be rendered, true by default
withControls.description_zh: 确定是否应呈现下一个/上一个控件，默认情况下为 true

withEdges.description: Determines whether first/last controls should be rendered, false by default
withEdges.description_zh: 确定是否应呈现第一个/最后一个控件，默认为 false

total.description: Total number of pages, must be an integer
